"\n"
"  C -->|\"explicit remove / GC / LRU<br/>dt_dev_pixelpipe_cache_remove()<br/>dt_dev_pixelpipe_cache_flush_old()<br/>dt_dev_pixel_pipe_cache_remove_lru()\"| G\n"
