#: content/contribute/website/index.md:252
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{{</* compare after=\"./img-after.jpg\" before=\"./img-before.jpg\" */>}}\n"
"Your slider legend goes here.\n"
"{{</* /compare */>}}\n"
