"{{< quote author=\"Ansel Adams\" >}}\n"
"The negative is the score, and the print is the performance.\n"
"{{< /quote >}}\n"
msgstr ""
"{{< quote author=\"Ansel Adams\" >}}\n"
"Negatyw jest partyturą, a odbitka jest wykonaniem.\n"
"{{< /quote >}}\n"

# TRANSLATOR Claude
